Raise an Ally's Crystal STR LV to 80

*Crystal strength may be raised after clearing "1-8 The Dark Forest Pt. 1" in Ch. 1: Primus Island.
From the menu, tap Enhancements.
Tap Crystal Strength on the Enhancements screen to open a screen where you can raise your characters' crystal strength.
Tap the character whose crystal strength you'd like to raise.
How far you can strengthen a character with the crystals you have will be indicated by a red glow.
Select the level to which you'd like to strengthen, and then tap Yes.
The character's crystal strength will be raised to that level, including any levels up to that point.
Each type of crystal can be obtained from cycle quests, which may be undertaken after clearing the first chapter, Primus Island.
